## Image Source Field

A field that stores an image sourced from either a URL or a linked file upload. The edit template provides a tabbed interface to switch between input modes; the embedded template renders the resolved image.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import ImageSourceField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/image-source';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field photo = contains(ImageSourceField);
}
```
